The expression in the image is a part of a mathematical problem involving the calculation of the value of $x$ in the equation $x^2 - 3 = 2$. To write it in LaTeX format, we can use the following code:

$$
\begin{aligned}
x^2 - 3 & = 2 \\
x^2 & = 5 \\
x & = \sqrt{5}
\end{aligned}
$$

This LaTeX code represents the steps taken to solve the equation $x^2 - 3 = 2$ and find the value of $x$.

